reviews.text: The food wasn't particularly impressive (such as the pasta) but the establishment is very spacious. You'll be better off ordering a sandwich or burger since it's hard to go wrong with them. Their risotto was pretty okay actually for a restaurant that doesn't specialize in Italian cuisine. Good for hanging out and watching sports with your friends. The bar also has a good assortment of draft beer.
Nice environment! Good service! I love the burger and the buffalo wings! Juicy and delicious!
A nice restaurant in Wanchai where you could have awesome dining experience and watching sports at the same.  The salad is delicious and the taste of ice coffee is impressive.
Nice local pub. Not cheap. Like most pubs here. They do a good lunch time set menu.
